{"tid":2137642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(分享喜悅）前排做外賣師識左個同事，賣料幾勁的","createTime":"2020-08-03T05:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T03:32:36.000Z","uid":2300,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26e7f58754f23824f53f3510a8f8325f8044236d","tid":2137642,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"前排轉行做deliveroo外賣師，係譚仔等外賣個陣識左位師兄，吹左半粒鐘原來佢last day<br />\n<br />\n佢話賭波都賺死，仲做乜撚野外賣，跟手成碗譚仔丟撚左落地，我嚇到叫左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後交換左IG，上星期開始跟佢買，今個星期已經係屋企數住錢叫deliveroo食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，好野真係要分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇番d follower 原來好多南亞同事都跟佢搵食，上左岸了。 <br />\n<br />\n做人做袋鼠，自己揀！ <br />\n<br />\n[member]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n449cX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn449cX8.jpg&h=344285ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Guvz8wu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuvz8wu.png&h=7720f327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/mem]..."},{"pid":"c63c1f5ce3f352cd969e05f9af39dc8deaa7a6f9","tid":2137642,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">閱</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bee742cf1cd37055a21682ec1cc762bb8aa5fdd","tid":2137642,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7200bbdeac3d2f0e580dbe52894670858fafe7","tid":2137642,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63c1f5ce3f352cd969e05f9af39dc8deaa7a6f9","tid":2137642,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">閱</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-